---
/* Cible Section — Target audience profiles */
---

<section id="cible" class="bg-glacial-bg py-[var(--spacing-section-gap)]">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Left: Deconstructed border block -->
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <div class="deconstructed-border p-12 lg:p-20 bg-glacial-surface overflow-hidden relative">
          <!-- Decorative blur -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-1/2 bg-indigo/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
          <h2
            class="relative font-display text-[length:var(--font-size-h1)] font-black tracking-tighter leading-none uppercase text-clinical-dark"
          >
            CE BOOTCAMP<br />
            <span class="text-gradient">EST FAIT POUR TOI.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="relative text-lg text-on-surface-muted max-w-md mt-6">
            Tu te reconnais dans un de ces profils&nbsp;? Alors on a construit ce programme pour toi.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: 4 profile items -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 reveal-right">

        <!-- Profile 1 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-8 group reveal delay-1">
          <span
            class="text-5xl font-black text-glacial-surface group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors font-display shrink-0"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            01
          </span>
          <div class="pt-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-2 text-clinical-dark font-display">
              Freelances en activit&eacute;
            </h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-muted text-base">
              Tu veux ajouter l'IA et l'automation &agrave; ton offre pour facturer plus et livrer plus vite.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Profile 2 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-8 group reveal delay-2">
          <span
            class="text-5xl font-black text-glacial-surface group-hover:text-indigo transition-colors font-display shrink-0"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            02
          </span>
          <div class="pt-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-2 text-clinical-dark font-display">
              Profils en reconversion
            </h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-muted text-base">
              Tu quittes un CDI et tu veux te lancer avec une comp&eacute;tence qui recrute.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Profile 3 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-8 group reveal delay-3">
          <span
            class="text-5xl font-black text-glacial-surface group-hover:text-cyan transition-colors font-display shrink-0"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            03
          </span>
          <div class="pt-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-2 text-clinical-dark font-display">
              Consultants &amp; coachs
            </h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-muted text-base">
              Tu accompagnes des entreprises et tu veux int&eacute;grer l'automation dans tes prestations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Profile 4 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-8 group reveal delay-4">
          <span
            class="text-5xl font-black text-glacial-surface group-hover:text-indigo transition-colors font-display shrink-0"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            04
          </span>
          <div class="pt-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-2 text-clinical-dark font-display">
              Agences &amp; &eacute;quipes
            </h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-muted text-base">
              Tu veux former ton &eacute;quipe aux outils d'automatisation et d'IA.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
